public class JTextFieldDoubleTableCellRenderer
extends JTextFieldDouble
implements javax.swing.table.TableCellRenderer, java.io.Serializable

A TableCellRenderer that wraps a JTextFieldDouble into a table make for easy highlighting of NaN's etc

This code was developed by NASA, Goddard Space Flight Center, Code 588 for the Scientist's Expert Assistant (SEA) project.
